I kinda find it funny that for months people have bitched about how much Al'Kabor sucks... then he starts passing out this amazing item which people were like &quot;OMG OMG l337&quot; when they saw it... and now that you don't have it (using you in general) you're pissed off!<br>
<br>
Relax, look at the big picture, it doesn't make you a better Wizard, it doesn't powerlevel you, it isn't <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> that amazing</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  Congratulate the people who got the staff, stop bitching at Verant for giving out an uber item that <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> you</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> didn't get, and shut the hell up already.  It's a god damn game, these items aren't real.  Stop stressing yourself out over 1s and 0s.  FFS!<br>
<br>
One lucky Wizard got this staff.  It wasn't all 60s.  Verant wasn't bias.  If you had gotten the staff (again, you in general) you wouldn't be posting in this thread.  This is a great item.  It was an artifact.  There are lots of great items that are artifacts.  It is in no way a 'fix' for the Wizard class.<br>
<br>
I think that...<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> ...JEALOUSY HAS RAISED IT'S UGLY HEAD YET AGAIN!!!  CONGRATULATE AND BE HAPPY FOR YOUR FELLOW WIZARD!!!</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Another thing, IMO this should have gone almost exclusivly to Wizards 52-58.  It's much more useful and beneficial to them than 59 and 60s.  Mana Regen for Soloing / Grouping is more useful than mana regen for raids / sitting on your ass / farming.  *SHRUGS*<br>
<br>
In closing, congrats to the people that got the scepter and sorry you have to listen to people bitch because they didn't get what you have.  Oh and on a side note, camping in GD for this item was in a word lame.  My commentary, if you don't like it sit on my epic and spin!  Thx~<br>
<br>
Yes, I've been dying to say this for weeks.<br>
